{"tid":673040,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"保險佬請入：老母懷疑食物中毒，回港先就醫","createTime":"2018-05-21T13:14:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T15:32:08.000Z","uid":55431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f71ea861439fc0fc194f689ce4b177759d6c83cd","tid":673040,"uid":55431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:14:45.000Z","msg":"老母跟團去馬來西亞新加坡<br />\n最後一日有兩位團友係當地都痾嘔<br />\n當日只係食過跟團既早午餐 下午3-4 點就到機場返港<br />\n<br />\n佢上到機先開始發作，返到香港連續痾嘔左四日<br />\n而且落機第二日馬上睇西醫  四日內睇左兩次<br />\n岩岩頂唔順入左私家住院抽血驗糞便<br />\n<br />\n我睇返經旅行社買既保險有寫<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/211052_73762bd7f4f7c60e8c90ed85a76a6604.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F211052_73762bd7f4f7c60e8c90ed85a76a6604.png&h=09815e26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n要係當地睇醫生先得，但當時根本都未發病<br />\n係上到飛機先開始唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n係有兩個團友都有事情況下 應該唔算係老母個人問題<br />\n有無方法可以向旅行社/ 保險公司索償"},{"pid":"1ec0d4acfb9f9ce6510e574a74206dcbafccb0c5","tid":673040,"uid":154725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:36:53.000Z","msg":"既然你都睇到t&amp;c寫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6877efbb4485e8080f945d136b167a111549faa1","tid":673040,"uid":129924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:39:27.000Z","msg":"直接打去保險公司問啦<br />\n依加真係咩都第一時間上連登開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f865ecb6c8628989cdefaf5cf7bee513f55a72","tid":673040,"uid":133959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:52:01.000Z","msg":"你跟團買應該問番旅行社，如果旅行社肯Endorse就乜都有得傾<br />\n否則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e582d5fc478c90aab08460655d937e3385666a26","tid":673040,"uid":2327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:23:38.000Z","msg":"買保險唔搵保險公司買，真係好on9😂😂"},{"pid":"b19ecfaad47aa28e3f46ada92baae96e6ac8fb77","tid":